data.description: This highly sought-after 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom ranch home boasts a split floor plan that provides both privacy and comfort. High ceilings, open-concept living, and continuous flooring can be found throughout the interior. Located in a well-established neighborhood and on the culdesac, this .7 acre lot includes a fenced-in backyard for added privacy and security. The outdoor space also includes a firepit, ideal for cozy evenings spent under the stars. Just minutes from I-85, shopping, and schools this home won't be available for long so schedule your showing today!
